-box;"><path style="box-sizing: border-box;" d="M135.7,2.3c0,0.6-0.5,1.1-1.1,1.1s-1.1-0.5-1.1-1.1c0-0.6,0.5-1.1,1.1-1.1S135.7,1.7,135.7,2.3z" fill="rgb(0,2,103)"></path></g><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><path style="box-sizing: border-box;" d="M131.3,2.3c0,0.6-0.5,1.1-1.1,1.1c-0.6,0-1.1-0.5-1.1-1.1c0-0.6,0.5-1.1,1.1-1.1    C130.8,1.2,131.3,1.7,131.3,2.3z" fill="rgb(0,2,103)"></path></g></g></svg></p></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="margin-top: -30px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 195.438px;vertical-align: top;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 2, 103);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">目录</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>1&nbsp; &nbsp; 民营企业排行全景图</strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>2 &nbsp;&nbsp; 百强民企画像：门槛提高，头部格局稳定</strong></span></strong></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual;mso-no-proof:yes;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>3 &nbsp;&nbsp; 增长先锋榜：31家企业排名进步，<strong style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;text-indent: 34px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(2, 30, 170);line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">新能源民企进步明显</span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>4 &nbsp;&nbsp; 新晋榜：16家民企进退洗牌</strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>5&nbsp; &nbsp; 启示与建议</strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;"></span></strong></span></p><div style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 530.475px;box-shadow: 